    - rid: 9129764407459971342
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r003_c03
        label: "R3 C3 Narrator: You step into your mentor's offi\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You step into your mentor's office and instantly spot an old floor-to-ceiling
          bookcase packed with books in all the languages this world speaks.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r004_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971343
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r004_c03
        label: "R4 C3 Narrator: Before you get a chance to study\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Before you get a chance to study it, Shinrai invites you to take a
          seat.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r005_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971344
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r005_c03
        label: "R5 C3 Shinrai: Greetings, scholar. I am pleased\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Greetings, scholar. I am pleased to welcome you to the Order of Labyrinth.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r006_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971345
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r006_c03
        label: "R6 C3 Shinrai: A faculty renowned for its think\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 6
        sfxId: 
        text: A faculty renowned for its thinkers and strategists, we take pride
          in our academic achievements and the foresight that we provide to the academy.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r007_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971346
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r007_c03
        label: "R7 C3 Narrator: You look at your mentor. He is s\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You look at your mentor. He is serious and distant, but there's a hint
          of pride in his voice.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r008_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971347
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r008_c03
        label: "R8 C3 You: No wonder. Shinrai puts a lot of\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: No wonder. Shinrai puts a lot of his time into making sure the faculty
          stays at the top of Chronosoul's academic ratings.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_line_r009_c03
    - rid: 9129764407459971348
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: chapter_1_line_r009_c03
        label: "R9 C3 Shinrai: Do you have any questions you wo\u2026"
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Do you have any questions you would like to ask? Now is the perfect
          time to do so.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: chapter_1_choice_r010_c03
